{"tid":826001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：高鐵、港珠澳大橋安然無恙「我們好大安慰」","createTime":"2018-09-18T02:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T03:53:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":391,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"1d457a7e412ce5ea97d333ce16c4786a4f81c6d1","tid":826001,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00001/28d3e612dcae72f8831873d2a5b6f7dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F28d3e612dcae72f8831873d2a5b6f7dc.jpg&h=df4fa8db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風「山竹」吹襲後，香港多處損毀，交通大混亂。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前表示，在這樣的大風下香港能夠保持基本穩妥，很快便恢復，「我會繼續形容為安然度過」，某程度上亦有一點點運氣。<br />\n<br />\n她又特別提到，今次事件中「令人比較安慰」是高鐵香港段及港珠澳大橋大體安然無恙，「這兩個這麼重大基建，今次受到超強颱風考驗，大體上安然無恙，當然有一點滲水、告示牌受損，但從基建角度，是經得起這個考驗，好安全，給予我們好大安慰」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥並再次衷心感謝颱風期間執勤人員的辛勞。"},{"pid":"5ceb4b036a527d342831272bd54e0ce124f5e791","tid":826001,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537237090130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537237090130&d=9m%2FyOCgkafFPAhLMJX9bngRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3f33cd5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537237090130&h=8253783a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537237090130</a>"},{"pid":"2cdb897bb9233f5180549cfce7a73ac9c1b91461","tid":826001,"uid":166725,"like":218,"dislike":3,"score":215,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"唔係應該㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=